cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.CR

The paper proposes a method for training supervised classification models mainly by un-labeled data, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method involves correcting errors in the weak classifiers, which could also be related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper mentions testing the method on little data sets, which could be related to cryptography and security (cs.CR).
